people can relate to.  I think these network sites are helping the non computer user become a little more computer friendly!</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-2511\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-2511\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/60d2eb55a8e9fcf5282a548f6171bb33?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/60d2eb55a8e9fcf5282a548f6171bb33?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.karate-mart.com/sparring-gear.html' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>sparring gear</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-2511\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2008-11-24T11:18:13-07:00\">November 24, 2008 at 11:18 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>These lots of companies are looking to cash in on these social networking sites.  At the end of 2008 there will be an estimated 2,000 of these sites up and functional.  Internet marketing and networking is on a climb and who knows when its going to stop?</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-2976\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-2976\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/df4ccd6bc9b82dcc648d86ff85343d89?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/df4ccd6bc9b82dcc648d86ff85343d89?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.commissionblueprint20.org' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Susan Warlington</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-2976\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-08-21T02:44:10-07:00\">August 21, 2009 at 2:44 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>This looks to be a great project, I hope they manage it all the way. Social networking is definately here to stay.</p>\n<p>Browsing the net the other day, I found a great resource on affiliate marketing as a business model, I found this site: </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.commissionblueprint20.org\" rel=\"nofollow\">Commission Blueprint 2</a> </p>\n<p>Might be a good thing to even out expensive loans.</p>\n<p>Take care</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-2995\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-2995\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ca37037e888557e53bbc5b63d9a1f622?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ca37037e888557e53bbc5b63d9a1f622?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://CommissionBlueprint2z.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Jeff Wayne</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-2995\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-08-26T21:33:41-07:00\">August 26, 2009 at 9:33 pm</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>It turns out that $100 laptop is not as popular as I expected. The good news is that it increase competition. I think it is the main reason we have netbook today. After google launch chrome operating system for netbook, more people will enjoy computing facility.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3002\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3002\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a4befebe29e0c60a4a7af97a35e6229c?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a4befebe29e0c60a4a7af97a35e6229c?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.commissionblueprint20review.net/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Glida John</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3002\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-08-28T08:13:14-07:00\">August 28, 2009 at 8:13 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>social networks still have to improving due to spamming and educating the real benefits to all user.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3006\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3006\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/db737ad0c99a043d83e1041444f7526b?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/db737ad0c99a043d83e1041444f7526b?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.commissionblueprint-two.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Commission Blueprint Two</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3006\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-08-30T14:24:23-07:00\">August 30, 2009 at 2:24 pm</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Hi.</p>\n<p>Ther is a very new service called Posterous. You can send emails, voice, videos and a lot of other informations to it. And the service will automatically forward everything to all your accounts.<br />\nThis is really helpful if you try to stay in touch with a lot of people.</p>\n<p>Pete</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3008\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3008\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84a60efb30d6e71665a05a6519f830f0?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/84a60efb30d6e71665a05a6519f830f0?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://aggressiveaffiliates.info' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Aggressive Affiliates</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3008\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-09-01T00:17:02-07:00\">September 1, 2009 at 12:17 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>I do agree that creating computer-based social networks for less privileged people is a great idea.  I believe many people from emerging countries are talented.  Technology could be the answer to make things great for emerging countries.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3017\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3017\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/120413496463b24e2a0a51f931b04943?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/120413496463b24e2a0a51f931b04943?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://commissionblueprint2truth.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Commission Blueprint 2</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3017\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-09-04T08:39:44-07:00\">September 4, 2009 at 8:39 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>This shows that technology can bring people together.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3019\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3019\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a7b647e17bb6cd09aa2f8296fee419b0?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a7b647e17bb6cd09aa2f8296fee419b0?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.realestateradiousa.com/commissionblueprint' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Commission Blueprint 2.0</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3019\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-09-04T22:59:47-07:00\">September 4, 2009 at 10:59 pm</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>Not only needed but I think it is a great idea for social media to be afforded to those at all corners of the globe!</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3033\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3033\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5bc525e69733095a62453a05d1f33422?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5bc525e69733095a62453a05d1f33422?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://wwwcommissionblueprint2.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Commission Blueprint 2</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3033\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-09-12T08:39:23-07:00\">September 12, 2009 at 8:39 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>To help make emerging countries better would be to use computer based social networks which I do agree.  Having friends and travelled to many of these countries I realized that there are so many talented people in these countries it is too bad so many do not realize this. It will be great to see more people connected this way.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3173\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3173\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1e627f6282bf98170bb3010a4e1f1ba0?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1e627f6282bf98170bb3010a4e1f1ba0?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www/my-estore.net/blog' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>eBay Affiliate</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3173\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2009-11-12T23:36:35-07:00\">November 12, 2009 at 11:36 pm</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>With so many companies, hospitals and schools replenishing old computer systems for new. There are plenty of computers that could be giving to less fortunate people or countries. The problem in some cases would be the lack of power and above all the lack of access to the internet.</p>\n<p>Social networks or any other internet median would be a lost cause in this case BUT with access to the internet. This would be most definately something worth persueing.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment even thread-even depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-3661\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-3661\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fcee7d8566554ef6f7765c6ecc9c6e4f?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fcee7d8566554ef6f7765c6ecc9c6e4f?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.squidoo.com/fast-money-making' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>www.squidoo.com/fast-money-making</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-3661\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2010-06-07T10:04:13-07:00\">June 7, 2010 at 10:04 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=\"comment-content comment\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>I was raised in a small village, where lots of kids ended up badly, wiothout a job or any hope for them for better life and think of people who are in even worse situation living in slums or africa. I think everyone should have a right for the information and information technology with social networking techniques should be possible for anyone.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section><!-- .comment-content -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"reply\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div><!-- .reply -->\n\t\t</article><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t</li><!-- #comment-## -->\n\t<li class=\"comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1\" id=\"li-comment-5931\">\n\t\t<article id=\"comment-5931\" class=\"comment\">\n\t\t\t<header class=\"comment-meta comment-author vcard\">\n\t\t\t\t<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dc5522131a68c20ac53b5acb809795f5?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dc5522131a68c20ac53b5acb809795f5?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite class=\"fn\"><a href='http://www.picowiki.com/bestgarciniacambogiainfo/index.php' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>pure garcinia cambogia</a> </cite><a href=\"https://ngs.ics.uci.edu/social-networks-for-less-privileged/#comment-5931\"><time pubdate datetime=\"2013-08-03T03:22:48-07:00\">August 3, 2013 at 3:22 am</time></a>\t\t\t</header><!-- .comment-meta -->\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<section class=